            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character fixates so hard on their target that they miss everything else\u2014like the wind, a moving foe, or that tree in the way. Their narrow focus turns a simple shot into a fiasco as arrows clang off unexpected obstacles. Peripheral awareness? They\u2019ve never heard of it. Accuracy takes a backseat to obsession.",
